---
title: Baked Mango Chutney Chicken with Roasted Veggies and Cilantro Rice
description: Busy night? This Indian-inspired dinner has it all: sweet curry sauce with a touch of spice, fragrant rice with peas and roasted veggies. Better yet, it comes together in 30 mins!
